description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 68, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 136, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 2 for East, 1 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [136 Votes, Top 15% Score]
